{"title":"深入老区（组诗）","authors":["凌翼"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深入老区（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凌翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书生毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾用秋收起义的重锤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂了一下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的耳朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次感到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震惊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鹃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争年代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山这张弓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射出无数箭一样的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也射出了将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少有名和无名的英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒在枪林弹雨下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当杜鹃盛开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有多少英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堵老墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残留着一位红军战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刷下的标语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标语发表的那个年代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空正暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一堵墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是正义的板报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数弹孔记录着老墙的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人每围剿一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老墙就中弹受伤一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老墙站着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个多世纪了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍向世人叙述"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战火与硝烟"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}